Tag.name: Tag
Tag.description: A key and value pair. This data type is used as a request parameter in the SetTagsForResource action and a response element in the ListTagsForResource action.

value.name: value
value.description: A value assigned to a tag key.

TelemetryMetadata.name: TelemetryMetadata
TelemetryMetadata.description: The metadata about the Amazon Inspector application data metrics collected by the agent. This data type is used as the response element in the GetTelemetryMetadata action.

messageType.name: messageType
messageType.description: A specific type of behavioral data that is collected by the agent.

count.name: count
count.description: The count of messages that the agent sends to the Amazon Inspector service.

dataSize.name: dataSize
dataSize.description: The data size of messages that the agent sends to the Amazon Inspector service.

TimestampRange.name: TimestampRange
TimestampRange.description: This data type is used in the AssessmentRunFilter data type.

beginDate.name: beginDate
beginDate.description: The minimum value of the timestamp range.

endDate.name: endDate
endDate.description: The maximum value of the timestamp range.

resourceArn.name: resourceArn
resourceArn.description: The ARN of the assessment template that is used during the event for which you want to stop receiving SNS notifications.

event.name: event
event.description: The event for which you want to stop receiving SNS notifications.
